1
00:00:05,802 --> 00:00:08,498
<i>Press down hard on the gas</i>

2
00:00:08,571 --> 00:00:12,439
<i>That's right, there's no compromise</i>

3
00:00:12,509 --> 00:00:16,502
<i>We'll slip through the night</i>

4
00:00:16,846 --> 00:00:19,337
<i>At the final moment push hard</i>

5
00:00:19,416 --> 00:00:23,477
<i>That's right, all the way to zero,</i>

6
00:00:23,553 --> 00:00:27,512
<i>Until we wipe away the days</i>

7
00:00:28,992 --> 00:00:33,725
<i>Gently open your heart</i>

8
00:00:34,431 --> 00:00:37,400
<i>If you pull it close to you</i>

9
00:00:39,836 --> 00:00:41,929
<i>It will reach you, without a doubt</i>

10
00:00:42,672 --> 00:00:43,969
<i>It will come, closer</i>

11
00:00:44,307 --> 00:00:46,867
<i>Now</i>

12
00:00:54,918 --> 00:01:00,288
<i>We're speeding through life,</i>
<i>squeezing it for all of its worth</i>

13
00:01:00,490 --> 00:01:01,650
<i>Our feet are tied</i>

14
00:01:01,724 --> 00:01:05,524
<i>But we still keep going farther</i>

15
00:01:05,862 --> 00:01:11,061
<i>Even if I take it back, and grasp it</i>

16
00:01:11,334 --> 00:01:12,665
<i>If you're not the one</i>

17
00:01:12,735 --> 00:01:14,134
<i>There will be no meaning</i>

18
00:01:14,204 --> 00:01:20,473
<i>And so we'll go far off into the distance.</i>

19
00:01:46,439 --> 00:01:47,269
Sasuke!

20
00:01:48,641 --> 00:01:51,109
Naruto's certainly different
from you, Sasuke.

21
00:01:51,177 --> 00:01:53,577
He's a klutz and kind of gets in the way.

22
00:01:53,646 --> 00:01:56,513
But he's not in the least a coward!

23
00:01:57,216 --> 00:01:59,081
Right? Isn't that's right?!

24
00:02:00,353 --> 00:02:01,183
Sasuke!

25
00:02:13,933 --> 00:02:15,958
<i>You foolish little brother.</i>

26
00:02:16,669 --> 00:02:20,765
<i>If you want to kill me, resent me,</i>
<i>hate me and...</i>

27
00:02:21,374 --> 00:02:24,639
<i>continue to live your ugly life.</i>

28
00:02:26,646 --> 00:02:27,374
<i>No...</i>

29
00:02:30,850 --> 00:02:31,817
<i>Flee.</i>

30
00:02:31,884 --> 00:02:35,285
<i>Flee and hang on to your life.</i>

31
00:02:36,255 --> 00:02:37,347
<i>No!</i>

32
00:02:41,093 --> 00:02:41,957
No!

33
00:02:45,464 --> 00:02:51,369
<i>The Sharingan Revived.</i>
<i>Dragon Flame Jutsu!</i>

34
00:02:54,240 --> 00:02:56,174
Just what I expect of the Uchiha clan...

35
00:02:56,576 --> 00:02:58,976
His blood has begun to stir...

36
00:03:00,379 --> 00:03:04,145
I should take my time and
confirm his true power.

37
00:03:06,652 --> 00:03:09,519
<i>I have to live so I can kill</i>
<i>my older brother...</i>

38
00:03:10,389 --> 00:03:11,378
<i>That's what I thought.</i>

39
00:03:12,959 --> 00:03:15,757
<i>But it's me who was being stupid.</i>

40
00:03:16,395 --> 00:03:17,123
<i>Naruto!</i>

41
00:03:17,196 --> 00:03:17,924
<i>Sakura!</i>

42
00:03:18,264 --> 00:03:20,789
<i>How can someone who can't put</i>
<i>his life on the line at a place like this...</i>

43
00:03:20,867 --> 00:03:22,858
<i>beat that man?!</i>

44
00:03:48,861 --> 00:03:49,520
<i>I can see.</i>

45
00:04:04,777 --> 00:04:05,471
<i>I can see!</i>

46
00:04:07,446 --> 00:04:08,413
<i>I can see you!</i>

47
00:04:32,271 --> 00:04:33,465
It's pretty good...

48
00:04:33,806 --> 00:04:36,900
You foretell my movements and
your aim is sure.

49
00:04:38,110 --> 00:04:39,509
You can see my moves, can't you?

50
00:04:50,723 --> 00:04:52,213
<i>The sun will set soon...</i>

51
00:04:53,993 --> 00:04:55,290
<i>I must find him quickly!</i>

52
00:04:56,295 --> 00:04:59,753
<i>It will become completely dark</i>
<i>and my disadvantage will increase.</i>

53
00:05:02,435 --> 00:05:06,064
<i>But why in the world right now...</i>
<i>what's his goal?</i>

54
00:05:08,808 --> 00:05:09,638
<i>Well, that's fine...</i>

55
00:05:10,509 --> 00:05:13,842
<i>He came to this village.</i>
<i>I'll settle this here and now.</i>

56
00:05:27,193 --> 00:05:28,592
I got you!

57
00:05:55,654 --> 00:05:56,621
A substitution!

58
00:06:20,079 --> 00:06:20,943
Sasuke!

59
00:06:26,252 --> 00:06:28,447
Humph!
You are too easy.

60
00:06:29,121 --> 00:06:31,146
The Uchiha name is crying.

61
00:06:31,857 --> 00:06:32,824
That's okay.

62
00:06:32,958 --> 00:06:36,223
I'll just take my time and play
with you before I'll kill you.

63
00:06:37,563 --> 00:06:39,292
Like a worm.

64
00:06:57,683 --> 00:07:00,914
This is Sharingan Windmill Triple Attack!

65
00:07:10,096 --> 00:07:11,757
<i>Fire Style. Dragon Flame Jutsu.</i>

66
00:07:23,409 --> 00:07:24,603
He did it!

67
00:07:46,632 --> 00:07:47,599
Sasuke!

68
00:07:48,901 --> 00:07:49,697
You did it!

69
00:07:53,506 --> 00:07:54,404
Are you okay?

70
00:07:55,341 --> 00:07:56,330
Hang on.

71
00:08:10,923 --> 00:08:12,015
Paralysis?

72
00:08:13,159 --> 00:08:17,220
I didn't expect that you could use
Sharingan this much at your age.

73
00:08:18,063 --> 00:08:20,759
You are truly a member
of the Uchiha clan.

74
00:08:21,233 --> 00:08:23,963
I do want you, after all.

75
00:08:28,807 --> 00:08:30,638
You're definitely his brother.

76
00:08:31,110 --> 00:08:34,602
Your eyes hide more ability
than that Itachi.

77
00:08:35,114 --> 00:08:36,911
Who in the world are you?

78
00:08:42,655 --> 00:08:44,680
My name is Orochimaru...

79
00:08:45,391 --> 00:08:53,662
If you think you want to meet me again,
desperately run to the top of this test.

80
00:08:54,200 --> 00:08:56,100
- The Scroll!
- Defeat the three...

81
00:08:56,168 --> 00:08:58,659
Sound Village Ninja
under my control.

82
00:08:59,305 --> 00:09:01,364
You are not making sense at all!

83
00:09:01,840 --> 00:09:05,469
<i>We</i> don't want to see
your face ever again, got it?!

84
00:09:07,513 --> 00:09:09,242
That won't do.

85
00:09:17,523 --> 00:09:18,387
Sasuke!

86
00:09:35,474 --> 00:09:36,532
Sasuke!

87
00:09:37,042 --> 00:09:39,977
You, what did you do to Sasuke?

88
00:09:41,647 --> 00:09:43,911
I gave him a parting gift.

89
00:09:44,316 --> 00:09:47,149
Sasuke absolutely would
come look for me...

90
00:09:47,453 --> 00:09:49,284
Iooking for power.

91
00:09:49,955 --> 00:09:54,255
I enjoyed seeing your various powers.

92
00:10:06,338 --> 00:10:07,202
Sasuke!

93
00:10:10,009 --> 00:10:11,476
Hold on, Sasuke.

94
00:10:12,244 --> 00:10:13,040
C'mon!

95
00:10:21,620 --> 00:10:22,848
Sasuke...

96
00:10:29,528 --> 00:10:30,961
Sasuke, c'mon!

97
00:10:31,630 --> 00:10:32,790
Sasuke...

98
00:10:34,133 --> 00:10:35,327
Sasuke...

99
00:10:40,139 --> 00:10:41,436
Naruto!

100
00:10:41,640 --> 00:10:44,666
Sasuke's... Sasuke's!

101
00:10:46,345 --> 00:10:48,040
Naruto!

102
00:11:03,662 --> 00:11:04,754
What?

103
00:11:06,699 --> 00:11:08,667
What should I do?

104
00:11:37,241 --> 00:11:38,265
<i>I can feel it!</i>

105
00:11:51,855 --> 00:11:53,083
<i>He's close by.</i>

106
00:12:14,578 --> 00:12:15,875
It's been a while...

107
00:12:17,014 --> 00:12:17,844
Anko.

108
00:12:20,551 --> 00:12:21,950
You're level S class,

109
00:12:22,019 --> 00:12:24,214
an extremely dangerous person on
the most wanted list.

110
00:12:25,322 --> 00:12:28,587
That's why I'll kill you here
even if it costs my life.

111
00:12:29,326 --> 00:12:32,159
That is my duty as
your former subordinate

112
00:12:32,229 --> 00:12:36,359
who learned it all from you.
Isn't that right, Orochimaru?!

113
00:12:36,934 --> 00:12:37,832
No, you can't.

114
00:12:53,384 --> 00:12:54,646
Striking Shadow Snake!

115
00:13:02,259 --> 00:13:03,521
I won't let you escape.

116
00:13:24,948 --> 00:13:26,108
I got you.

117
00:13:27,084 --> 00:13:29,917
Orochimaru,
I'm gonna borrow your left hand.

118
00:13:31,722 --> 00:13:32,950
<i>This hand sign...</i>

119
00:13:34,258 --> 00:13:37,785
Right... you and I are going to die here.

120
00:13:41,365 --> 00:13:44,129
<i>Ninja Art. Twin Snakes Sacrifice</i>

121
00:13:46,170 --> 00:13:49,333
You intend to commit suicide?

122
00:14:00,984 --> 00:14:02,212
Substitution.

123
00:14:19,136 --> 00:14:22,936
As you are a Special Jonin
of the village,

124
00:14:23,407 --> 00:14:27,104
you can't be just using
the forbidden Jutsu I taught you.

125
00:14:30,714 --> 00:14:32,579
I told you it wouldn't work.

126
00:14:47,130 --> 00:14:48,620
Why have you come now?

127
00:14:48,966 --> 00:14:53,130
It's our reunion after so long,
and you're awfully cold.

128
00:14:54,571 --> 00:14:57,870
Don't tell me that you came
to assassinate Lord Hokage!?

129
00:14:58,208 --> 00:14:59,470
No, no...

130
00:15:00,277 --> 00:15:02,575
I don't have enough
subordinates for that yet...

131
00:15:03,080 --> 00:15:07,278
I've heard of the excellence ones of
this village and thought I'd put dibs on it.

132
00:15:12,623 --> 00:15:13,920
A little while ago,

133
00:15:13,991 --> 00:15:17,518
I gave that same Curse Mark
as a present.

134
00:15:19,096 --> 00:15:20,859
There's a kid that I want.

135
00:15:22,399 --> 00:15:24,094
Selfish as always.

136
00:15:24,568 --> 00:15:25,967
That kid will die.

137
00:15:26,970 --> 00:15:30,838
Certainly... the odds are 1 in 10
that he'll die,

138
00:15:31,174 --> 00:15:34,837
but he may survive just like you did.

139
00:15:35,913 --> 00:15:38,404
This kid, you really like him, huh?

140
00:15:40,183 --> 00:15:41,480
Are you jealous?

141
00:15:42,052 --> 00:15:42,916
Hey...

142
00:15:43,620 --> 00:15:47,852
Are you still holding a grudge
that I used you and threw you away?

143
00:15:50,794 --> 00:15:53,820
Unlike you, that kid will excel.

144
00:15:54,231 --> 00:15:57,962
For one thing he inherited
the Uchiha ability.

145
00:15:59,970 --> 00:16:04,304
He has beautiful features and is
a vessel who can become my heir.

146
00:16:05,108 --> 00:16:08,703
If that kid lived,
it will make things interesting.

147
00:16:09,479 --> 00:16:12,937
Be sure not to cancel this test.

148
00:16:15,085 --> 00:16:18,054
Three people from my village
are also under your care.

149
00:16:18,956 --> 00:16:20,685
Make me enjoy it.

150
00:16:23,427 --> 00:16:27,329
<i>If something happens to</i>
<i>deprive me of my fun,</i>

151
00:16:28,231 --> 00:16:30,995
<i>consider it the end of Leaf Village.</i>

152
00:16:43,146 --> 00:16:46,274
We've secured food and water after
spending half a day

153
00:16:46,717 --> 00:16:49,709
and now most teams have halted activity.

154
00:16:51,254 --> 00:16:53,722
As we planned,
this is the time that we attack.

155
00:16:54,191 --> 00:16:56,716
We'll split up into three and go scouting.

156
00:16:56,893 --> 00:17:00,420
However, whether we find
other teams or not,

157
00:17:00,864 --> 00:17:03,196
we return to this place.

158
00:17:04,568 --> 00:17:05,125
Got it?

159
00:17:05,736 --> 00:17:06,634
Okay.

160
00:17:06,737 --> 00:17:07,726
Roger.

161
00:17:08,538 --> 00:17:09,232
Okay.

162
00:17:09,640 --> 00:17:10,299
Scatter!

163
00:17:20,517 --> 00:17:23,008
His breathing is gradually
getting regular...

164
00:17:23,654 --> 00:17:25,679
but he still has a terrible fever.

165
00:17:37,267 --> 00:17:39,064
<i>I have to protect them both.</i>

166
00:17:53,684 --> 00:17:56,847
I have to communicate this
to Lord Hokage right away.

167
00:18:29,286 --> 00:18:31,379
Cripes! At a time like this!

168
00:19:01,384 --> 00:19:04,353
T-This is Paralysis Jutsu.

169
00:19:05,288 --> 00:19:07,279
So you are here, Anko.

170
00:19:18,101 --> 00:19:21,161
You're pretty late for Anbu Black Ops.

171
00:19:21,471 --> 00:19:22,802
Well, don't say that.

172
00:19:28,512 --> 00:19:29,877
Are you okay, hey?

173
00:19:30,413 --> 00:19:32,313
Huh? T-This is!

174
00:19:33,216 --> 00:19:35,013
The Curse Mark is appearing...

175
00:19:35,852 --> 00:19:36,750
Don't tell me?!

176
00:19:37,621 --> 00:19:38,645
Is it Orochimaru?

177
00:19:39,256 --> 00:19:40,951
What, really?

178
00:19:42,559 --> 00:19:45,255
Now that it's come to this,
we'll take you to Lord Hokage.

179
00:19:46,696 --> 00:19:48,459
No, take me to the tower.

180
00:19:48,899 --> 00:19:50,196
What are you saying?

181
00:19:50,600 --> 00:19:52,693
The moment Orochimaru comes
to this village

182
00:19:52,769 --> 00:19:54,327
a strict alert is issued.

183
00:19:54,738 --> 00:19:56,000
It's more urgent than
continuing the Exam.

184
00:19:56,506 --> 00:19:57,336
I know...

185
00:19:58,942 --> 00:20:03,311
Anyway, I'll tell the whole story later,
so please call for Lord Hokage.

186
00:20:15,859 --> 00:20:16,917
I found you.

187
00:20:17,661 --> 00:20:21,358
As Orochimaru ordered,
we'll wait for daybreak to do it.

188
00:20:22,399 --> 00:20:25,266
Sasuke Uchiha is our target,
not the other.

189
00:20:26,002 --> 00:20:29,460
If they come in the way,
it's okay to kill the other two, right?

190
00:20:29,906 --> 00:20:30,668
Of course.

191
00:21:05,453 --> 00:21:10,049
<i>Hey, can you hear it?</i>

192
00:21:10,157 --> 00:21:18,257
<i>The clear, blue sky goes on and on</i>

193
00:21:19,333 --> 00:21:27,866
<i>The ocean spans limitlessly</i>

194
00:21:28,476 --> 00:21:36,178
<i>Please keep that smile on your face forever</i>

195
00:21:37,585 --> 00:21:43,114
<i>Or else I'll cry</i>

196
00:21:43,190 --> 00:21:46,956
<i>You won't have to search around you</i>

197
00:21:47,028 --> 00:21:50,589
<i>It's all ok now.</i>

198
00:21:51,065 --> 00:21:59,473
<i>Everyone is inside</i>
<i>this hand</i>

199
00:21:59,874 --> 00:22:04,937
<i>when you want to cry, and you want to run away</i>

200
00:22:05,012 --> 00:22:09,415
<i>When you forget what happiness is</i>

201
00:22:09,583 --> 00:22:13,246
<i>Just sing.</i>

202
00:22:13,554 --> 00:22:18,651
<i>Light is born, and darkness was born</i>

203
00:22:18,793 --> 00:22:20,920
<i>The two are one</i>

204
00:22:21,028 --> 00:22:27,297
<i>Harmonia, feel the telepathy</i>

205
00:22:27,902 --> 00:22:32,896
<i>Hey, can you hear it?</i>

206
00:22:36,286 --> 00:22:39,653
The beautiful wild beast of Leaf Village
Rock Lee, is here!

207
00:22:40,223 --> 00:22:42,885
Yeah, I did it!
I did it, Guy Sensei!

208
00:22:42,959 --> 00:22:46,190
Now I can get Sakura's heart,
right on the mark!

209
00:22:48,098 --> 00:22:50,862
You could say, in terms of numbers,
the disadvantage is mine!

210
00:22:51,134 --> 00:22:53,227
But on the contrary,
the conditions have been met.

211
00:22:53,570 --> 00:22:57,472
Guy Sensei, I will use <i>that</i> technique
without hesitation.

212
00:22:58,408 --> 00:23:03,868
Next episode: " Bushy Brow's Pledge:
Undying Love and Protection!"
